Author: dzmiguel
Content:
Hey folks! Lemme introduce my self. I'm El, a 30-year-old single dude this year.

Right now, I'm freelancing and also driver to Grab/GoCar. 

I also kinda know my way around Jakarta, you know? Cool hangout spots, good eats, chill places, hidden gems, etc.

So yeah, I could totally be your Jakarta tour guide, especially if you're curious about riding public transport and hitting up those roadside "warteg" spots where you can eat for less than 15K. 'Cause I'm always hopping on public transport, I know the KRL, Busway, and MRT routes like the back of my hand.

Need a ride to the airport or a pickup from the airport? I can help you out with that too. Your personal chauffeur, right here! Or if you wanna explore Jakarta for the whole day, I'm down. Can even help lug your stuff around. 

Why roll with me instead of just using a ride-hailing app? Well, with me, you're guaranteed to get picked up on time. Clean car (it's a Toyota Rush, not a fancy ride but it's my personal car). No hassle, and you won't end up with some weirdo driver who'll just piss you off. You know how it is if you read the news ‚Äì lots of strange online drivers out there, all sorts of cases and stuff. It's 'cause the app takes a huge cut, stresses the drivers out, and makes it hard for them to make a living.

Plus, I can speak English, so I can be your chat buddy too!

Just hit me up if you're keen or wanna ask anything first.

Author: floatingtales
Content:
TEA SELECTION IS HERE!

Tenren teas

Tenren is the go-to premium tea brand in Taiwan, their signature teas are the king series of teas, pictured here. The king's series of teas blends Taiwanese Tall Mountain Oolong tea (gaoshan oolong), with premium ginseng for health benefits.

The kings tea series are graded by 2 things, the first number and the last number, the first number notes the quality of teas, graded, from lowest to highest like so: 1-9-3-4-5. The third number is the degree of roasting, with 3 being light roast, and 9 being the darker roast.
